 0.60)、吸毒3~5年(t = −2.15, P &lt; 0.05, d = 0.43)的戒毒人员。</p><table-wrap id="table2" ><label><xref ref-type="table" rid="table2">Table 2</xref></label><caption><title> ANOVA of Gender and HI</title></caption><table><tbody><thead><tr><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >差异来源</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >男</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >女</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >t</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >是HIV</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >否HIV</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >t</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >1年内</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >1-3年</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >3-5年</th><th align="center" valign="middle" >5年以上</th><th align="center" valign="middle"  rowspan="2"  >F</th></tr></thead><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >M &#177; SD</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >家庭支持</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >21.99 &#177; 4.58</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >21.10 &#177; 5.08</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.41</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >23.92 &#177; 3.12</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >21.69 &#177; 4.74</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >1.61</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >20.80 &#177; 6.39</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >22.44 &#177; 4.84</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >21.81 &#177; 4.42</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >21.52 &#177; 4.47</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >0.99</td></tr><tr><td align="center" valign="middle" >朋友支持</td><td align="center" valign="middle" >18.86 &#177; 4.